<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog</title>
    <link href="/css/blog.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="blog-container">
        <h1 class="blog-title">Blog</h1><br>

        <div class="blog-list">
            <div class="blog-item">
                <h2 class="blog-heading">The Secret to a Perfect Cake</h2>
                <p class="blog-description">Learn the best tips and tricks for baking a delicious and beautiful cake.</p>
                <button class="btn-primary" onclick="openModal('modal-1')">Read more</button>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-item">
                <h2 class="blog-heading">Our Favorite Cake Flavors</h2>
                <p class="blog-description">Discover the most popular cake flavors that our customers love.</p>
                <button class="btn-primary" onclick="openModal('modal-2')">Read more</button>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-item">
                <h2 class="blog-heading">How to Decorate a Cake Like a Pro</h2>
                <p class="blog-description">Step-by-step guide to decorating a cake with professional techniques.</p>
                <button class="btn-primary" onclick="openModal('modal-3')">Read more</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modals -->
    <div id="modal-1" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-box">
            <h2 class="modal-title">The Secret to a Perfect Cake</h2>
            <img class="modal-image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559329373-78f77851b979?q=80&w=2944&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="cake">
            <p class="modal-text">The secret to a perfect cake lies in meticulous detail, including using fresh ingredients at room temperature, precise measurements, properly lined pans, allowing cakes to cool completely before frosting, and a final chill in the fridge. <br><br>
                Here's a breakdown of key tips for baking a perfect cake:<br>
                1. Start with Quality Ingredients & Preparation<br>
                2. Cake Baking Techniques<br>
                3. Frosting and Decoration
            </p>
            <div class="modal-action">
                <button class="btn-primary" onclick="closeModal('modal-1')">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-2" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-box">
            <h2 class="modal-title">Our Favorite Cake Flavors</h2>
            <p class="modal-text">Read more about the most loved cake flavors by our customers.</p>
            <div class="modal-action">
                <button class="btn-primary" onclick="closeModal('modal-2')">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-3" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-box">
            <h2 class="modal-title">How to Decorate a Cake Like a Pro</h2>
            <p class="modal-text">Learn the best cake decorating techniques used by professionals.</p>
            <div class="modal-action">
                <button class="btn-primary" onclick="closeModal('modal-3')">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function openModal(id) {
            document.getElementById(id).classList.add("modal-open");
        }
        function closeModal(id) {
            document.getElementById(id).classList.remove("modal-open");
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
